***CC Amplifier Design Using NgSpice***


Step 1:Create File
Open terminal: type command below 
nano cc_amp.cir

Step 2:In GNU Dashboard Paste below Script

* Common Collector Amplifier

VCC vcc 0 DC 12
VIN in 0 SIN(0 0.1 1k)

R1 vcc base 100k
R2 base 0 47k

RE emitter 0 1k

CIN in base 10u
COUT emitter out 10u

Q1 vcc base emitter 2N3904

.model 2N3904 NPN(IS=6.734E-15 BF=255.9)

.tran 0.1ms 10ms

.control
run
plot v(in) v(out)
.endc

.end

Step 3:Run Simulation
ngspice cc_amp.cir

You can observe waveform and OutPut in Terminal.
